017package org.microbean.type;
018
019import java.lang.reflect.GenericDeclaration;
020import java.lang.reflect.TypeVariable;
021
022/**
023 * An {@link UnannotatedElement} that is also a stub implementation of
024 * the {@link GenericDeclaration} interface.
025 *
026 * @author <a href="https://about.me/lairdnelson"
027 * target="_parent">Laird Nelson</a>
028 *
029 * @see UnannotatedElement
030 */
031public final class NonexistentGenericDeclaration extends UnannotatedElement implements GenericDeclaration {
032
033
034  /*
035   * Static fields.
036   */
037
038
039  /**
040   * The sole {@link NonexistentGenericDeclaration} that can exist in
041   * a given Java virtual machine.
042   *
043   * @nullability This field is never {@code null}.
044   */
045  public static final NonexistentGenericDeclaration INSTANCE = new NonexistentGenericDeclaration();
046
047
048  /*
049   * Constructors.
050   */
051
052
053  private NonexistentGenericDeclaration() {
054    super();
055  }
056
057
058  /*
059   * Instance methods.
060   */
061
062
063  /**
064   * Returns an empty array when invoked.
065   *
066   * @return an empty {@link TypeVariable} array
067   */
068  @Override
069  public final TypeVariable<?>[] getTypeParameters() {
070    return AbstractType.EMPTY_TYPE_VARIABLE_ARRAY.clone();
071  }
072
073}
